@SpecificationDemo_HostAddress = http://localhost:5203

### 1. All active products (ActiveSpecification)
GET {{SpecificationDemo_HostAddress}}/products

### 2. Electronics only (ActiveSpecification AND CategorySpecification)
GET {{SpecificationDemo_HostAddress}}/products?category=Electronics

### 3. Books under £45 (ActiveSpecification AND CategorySpecification AND PriceRangeSpecification)
GET {{SpecificationDemo_HostAddress}}/products?category=Books&maxPrice=45

### 4. In-stock items across all categories (ActiveSpecification AND InStockSpecification)
GET {{SpecificationDemo_HostAddress}}/products?inStock=true

### 5. Featured in-stock items (all three specs composed)
GET {{SpecificationDemo_HostAddress}}/products?inStock=true&featured=true

### 6. Pre-composed: featured deals — Featured AND InStock AND Price <= £50
GET {{SpecificationDemo_HostAddress}}/products/featured-deals

### 7. Pre-composed: clearance — Active AND InStock AND NOT Featured AND Price <= £30
GET {{SpecificationDemo_HostAddress}}/products/clearance

### 8. Single product by id
GET {{SpecificationDemo_HostAddress}}/products/1
